The Presidential Palace of Turkey stated that it has reached an agreement with Sweden, Finland and NATO, and will continue to work on the steps of joining NATO in Sweden.

The Presidential Palace of Turkey pointed out that the permanent joint mechanism established under the framework of the Memorandum of understanding during the NATO Summit of Turkey, Finland and Sweden in 2022 has held the fourth meeting, and the senior consultant of the Turkish president also attended the meeting. Essence

